    <title>Mantrana</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ulink url="https://app.travis-ci.com/jatindalal/mantrana"><image type="html" name="https://app.travis-ci.com/jatindalal/mantrana.svg?branch=main" alt="Build Status" inline="yes"></image>
</ulink></para>
<para>Cross platform GUI desktop chat application made with QT</para>
<sect1 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Build</title>
<sect2 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md2">
<title>Dependencies</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Qt5 base and websocket packages</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Cmake version &gt;= 3.5</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>(Optionally) Ninja</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md3">
<title>Instructions</title>
<para>Make sure you have a C++ compiler and cmake can find QT5 config files.</para>
<sect3 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md4">
<title>Using Cmake</title>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>.<sp/>-B<sp/>&lt;build-directory&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>&lt;build-directory&gt;<sp/>-j<sp/>&lt;jobs&gt;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The number of jobs can be set in accordance with your cpu cores or can be ignored.</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md5">
<title>Using Cmake + Ninja</title>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>.<sp/>-B<sp/>&lt;build-directory&gt;<sp/>-G<sp/>Ninja</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>&lt;build-directory&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ninja</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md__home_arvindbis29__desktop_src_mantrana__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md6">
<title>Docker for server</title>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">docker<sp/>build<sp/>.<sp/>--tag<sp/>mantrana</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">docker<sp/>run<sp/>--rm<sp/>-itd<sp/>-p<sp/>8880:8880<sp/>\</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-v<sp/>$(pwd)/config:/home/mantrana/config<sp/>\</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-u<sp/>$(id<sp/>-u):$(id<sp/>-g)<sp/>\</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>mantrana</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</sect3>
